milestones.description: This is the highest match aggregate (379) involving teams Australia & South Africa in ODIs
Wessels and Hansie Cronje's 140-run partnership is SA's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 112 between Wessels and Peter Kirsten
